profile:
A small business with big passion

Cedar Ridge Carpentry owner James Reed, has over 10 years experience in exterior carpentry. Anyone who experiences James’ work would speak to his professionalism, work ethic, efficiency, and overall passion for what he does. At Cedar Ridge we take extreme care into the quality of work we produce, choosing the highest quality product for your budget, and taking great pride in what we create.

Contact us today for a free quote!
